This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with neural text generation tasks such as machine translation and image captioning. It may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes an algorithm to generate pseudo-references. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it specifically mentions image captioning. It may also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with natural language generation tasks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural text generation.
